                    <p>The <strong>RYA Start Yachting course</strong> offers a fun and practical introduction to sailing for complete beginners. Over just two days, you‚Äôll gain hands-on experience and build confidence aboard a cruising yacht. By the end of the course, you will have learned to steer, handle sails, tie basic knots, and understand key safety procedures.</p>

